    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
石田及下等士官水夫頭には、私より金少々遣し申候。弐拾金御つかはしになれば可なり。<lb />
西洋衣がとゝのい申候。彼横笛船では船将にて候得バ、<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">夫</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（それ）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>ばかりの事してやり度奉<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>存候。何れ御考奉<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>願候。再拝。<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em">八月廿五日<seg rend="chitsuki_1" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 1em">龍馬　再拝。</seg></seg>
<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_4" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 4em">佐々木先生</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_9" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 9em">左右</seg>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</seg></p></body>
